net.sf.expectit

Interface Result

  • All Superinterfaces:
    MatchResult
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MultiResult

    public interface Result
extends MatchResult
    A representation of the result of a single match operation.

    The interface contains methods to query the results of the match against an expression.
